{"tid":923090,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件返工見過同事犯罪嘅事","createTime":"2018-12-01T03:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T05:04:43.000Z","uid":140363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2351f9ae7c1f8c68713bf08c0093c0e6749dd1aa","tid":923090,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"以前返零售兼職 聽講班大佬講好多唔同鋪會耐唔時keep起啲單 唔入機 睇下當個月做唔做到銷售額 再決定留幾多 長期見到佢locker 有疊客用左未入嘅coupon 備用 <br />\n<br />\n結果維持左三幾年 比個突圍而出由店經理升左上office 嘅人清算曬 成班仲有做嘅就叫佢地自己辭職  聽講仲有班兼職鐘意將客比現金嘅單用自己信用卡碌儲分袋走啲cash 都一獲炒曬<br />\n<br />\n雖然間公司冇報警 但成班都抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737aa080e82f4b93e1ec45a22cba7f815813518c","tid":923090,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e4d239c01b7ad2b8a97786737073f2276705d81","tid":923090,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"老細一手撳啲女同事就喺枱頭屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0fee17ab79c15f0fade70ba43581cea081fe04","tid":923090,"uid":7903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"有同事拎假貨換走公司真貨賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再將偷返黎既公司真貨係出面賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n儲緊證據，即將報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998a32f727c099971e01293f4949383cd59e19b8","tid":923090,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb0fee17ab79c15f0fade70ba43581cea081fe04","tid":923090,"uid":7903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"有同事拎假貨換走公司真貨賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再將偷返黎既公司真貨係出面賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n儲緊證據，即將報串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g